<sect1 id="dir_9f1b63b16504459c7f769f041503636c_1autotoc_md91">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::combat::systems</title><para>Gameplay systems for combat mechanics processing.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_9f1b63b16504459c7f769f041503636c_1autotoc_md92">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module contains systems that process combat-related components each frame. Systems read component state and generate commands or modify world state accordingly.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_9f1b63b16504459c7f769f041503636c_1autotoc_md93">
<title>Key Classes</title><para><table rows="2" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="yes"><para>Class  </para>
