</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>ProjectileSpawnSystem</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Spawns projectiles for entities with active ShootComponents  </para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_9f1b63b16504459c7f769f041503636c_1autotoc_md94">
<title>System Flow</title><para>The <computeroutput>ProjectileSpawnSystem</computeroutput> operates as follows:</para>
<para>1. Queries entities with <computeroutput>ShootComponent</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>Aim2DComponent</computeroutput>, and <computeroutput>TranslationStateComponent</computeroutput> 2. Checks if shooting is active (intensity &gt; 0) and aim direction is valid 3. Calculates projectile velocity from source velocity and aim direction 4. Enqueues <computeroutput>SpawnCommand</computeroutput> with <computeroutput>EmitterContext</computeroutput> for deferred spawning</para>
